Title: 调用关系图
Describe: 覆盖 S06_CALL_RELATIONSHIPS。展示用户调用、agent graph、provider implementation、SDK/API、callback/streaming 的端到端路径。
------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
S06_CALL_RELATIONSHIPS - 从 agent 到 provider SDK

[Description]
典型调用链：用户调用 `create_agent(model="openai:...", tools=[...])`，工厂函数调用 `init_chat_model`，provider 解析后创建 `langchain_openai.ChatOpenAI`，agent graph 运行时调用 `BaseChatModel.invoke`/stream 相关方法，OpenAI partner 把 LangChain messages 转换为 provider payload，调用 OpenAI SDK，返回 `AIMessage`，如有 tool calls 再进入 `ToolNode`。

[UML]
@startuml
participant "用户代码" as User
participant "create_agent" as AgentFactory
participant "init_chat_model" as InitModel
participant "ChatOpenAI" as ChatOpenAI
participant "StateGraph" as Graph
participant "OpenAI SDK/API" as OpenAIAPI
participant "ToolNode" as ToolNode
participant "BaseTool 或 Callable" as Tool
User -> AgentFactory: create_agent(model, tools, middleware)
AgentFactory -> InitModel: init_chat_model(model)
InitModel --> AgentFactory: BaseChatModel
AgentFactory -> Graph: add_node model and tools
AgentFactory --> User: CompiledStateGraph
User -> Graph: stream or invoke messages
Graph -> ChatOpenAI: invoke messages
ChatOpenAI -> OpenAIAPI: request with converted messages
OpenAIAPI --> ChatOpenAI: assistant message or tool calls
ChatOpenAI --> Graph: AIMessage
alt AIMessage has tool_calls
  Graph -> ToolNode: route tool calls
  ToolNode -> Tool: execute selected tool
  Tool --> ToolNode: tool result
  ToolNode --> Graph: ToolMessage
  Graph -> ChatOpenAI: next model turn
else no tool_calls
  Graph --> User: final messages
end
@enduml

[Detail]
从用户代码开始读序列图。实线箭头表示同步或运行时调用，`alt` 块展示 agent 的停止条件。`create_agent` 本身不直接调用 OpenAI SDK，它只组装 graph；实际 provider I/O 发生在 `ChatOpenAI` 内部。工具路径由 LangGraph `ToolNode` 管理，但工具对象仍然来自用户提供的 `BaseTool`、callable 或 dict。维护风险是这条链跨越了用户代码、LangChain active package、partner package、provider API 和工具实现。

------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
标准测试调用链

[Description]
`langchain-tests` 让 partner 包用相同测试基类验证实现。`ChatModelUnitTests` 位于 `libs/standard-tests/langchain_tests/unit_tests/chat_models.py:276`，要求子类实现 `chat_model_class` 和 `chat_model_params`；`ChatModelIntegrationTests` 位于 integration tests 包约 178 行；OpenAI partner 的多个 standard test 文件继承这些基类。

[UML]
@startuml
participant "Partner test class" as PartnerTest
participant "ChatModelUnitTests" as UnitSuite
participant "ChatModelIntegrationTests" as IntegrationSuite
participant "Partner ChatModel" as ChatModel
participant "Provider API 或 VCR" as Provider
PartnerTest -> UnitSuite: inherit and provide class params
UnitSuite -> ChatModel: instantiate without live network
UnitSuite --> PartnerTest: assert contract behavior
PartnerTest -> IntegrationSuite: optional live or recorded tests
IntegrationSuite -> ChatModel: invoke model operations
ChatModel -> Provider: HTTP through SDK when enabled
Provider --> ChatModel: model response
IntegrationSuite --> PartnerTest: assert integration behavior
@enduml

[Detail]
箭头表示测试执行和被测对象实例化。unit suite 强调无网络、确定性和接口行为；integration suite 允许 live API 或 VCR 录制。由于 provider 包很多，标准测试是防止每个 integration 自行解释 core 契约的关键机制。风险是当 core 添加新能力时，标准测试和 partner 覆盖必须同步，否则某些 provider 会静默缺少能力。
